# ClawRoom — Environment template
#
# This project is two deployments. Neither requires server-side env vars
# from this file in production:
#
#   apps/edge/    → Cloudflare Worker. Env vars are in apps/edge/wrangler.toml
#                  and Cloudflare dashboard secrets, NOT here.
#   apps/monitor/ → Cloudflare Pages. Build-time only, no runtime env.
#
# Local development overrides for the monitor (optional):
#   VITE_API_TARGET=http://127.0.0.1:8787   # point monitor at a local edge worker
